{"tid":1270054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話說我識咗一個水上人朋友，佢老豆啱啱過身。","createTime":"2019-06-30T17:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:01:16.000Z","uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d5da43ee3cb00fd718bfb80dfa4a214a9b70dd6a","tid":1270054,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"嗰日經開西貢買蝦醬俾家中兩老，經過有檔個檔主係90後，出於好奇就同佢嗲咗幾句。<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    90後檔主：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：「依，好少可見咁後生既賣海味乾貨喎。」<br />\n<br />\n90後檔主：「我阿爸啱啱過咗身，留咗隻艇俾我。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「呃，對唔住，節哀順變。」<br />\n<br />\n90後檔主：「唔緊要，你有心啦。係個海上面搵食，都預咗會咁。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「令尊翁係出意外身故既？」<br />\n<br />\n90後檔主：「係打魚時候出意外既，唔單止我老豆，我舅父，表哥，阿爺，都係魂斷大海。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「吓，既然個海咁危險，點解唔返上岸上面做下小生意搵食呢？」<br />\n<br />\n90後檔主：「大海雖然危險，但係勤力少少都叫搵到兩餐，但係呢個殺人政權，官官相衛，小市民都兩餐都搵唔到。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我寧願對住呢個怒海都好過對住個政府。<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢到我就嚇到走咗，想問下連登仔點樣可以追返佢找少俾我嗰幾十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24d13ec1c2283577738d669adf6cd78aa470d04","tid":1270054,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1c018162a9bd7f0cb8a60cf9a71d8837a98b23","tid":1270054,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"Sorry 開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd6fd0edcad3156c6debbe3e0da26edfa6c38f1","tid":1270054,"uid":85390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a24d13ec1c2283577738d669adf6cd78aa470d04","tid":1270054,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"夜晚佢家人會拎比你，係張床耐心等下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357ba981149d876315fc346f35682054d3f00db3","tid":1270054,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd6fd0edcad3156c6debbe3e0da26edfa6c38f1","tid":1270054,"uid":85390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a24d13ec1c2283577738d669adf6cd78aa470d04","tid":1270054,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"夜晚佢家人會拎比你，係張床耐心等下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}